main event: An unidentified object was tracked at Wheelus AFB, Morocco, observed moving at varying speeds.
interesting points: The object was sighted at an azimuth of 95-100 degrees., The object changed speed from 75 knots to 50 knots after 110 miles., The object faded at a distance of 55 miles., The total duration of the sighting was 12 minutes., The characteristics indicated suggested it was likely an airplane.
